{
  "stem": "25591.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the current governor of New York, Governor Pataki, is of Hungarian background.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He has had no relationship with Hungary and he took his first trip to Hungary, I think, last year, to a village.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I met with him at a-- at a-- at a Yom HaShoah event in New York, and we had a very nice conversation.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I understand that he's a very decent fellow, and he went to his village, and-- and-- but he really has had no Hungarian, really.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He doesn't speak Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I am the other Hungarian-American who politically has a position.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] ironically, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] there are probably two Hungarian-Americans who are very well known in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One, because he has done an enormous amount for Hungary through his foundations, and that's my friend George Soros, who is a multi-billionaire and has done unbelievably impressive things for free and open societies beginning in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I just had lunch with him last week, and we were good friends.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He has done an incredible amount for Hungary through his philanthropy, which is very intelligent philanthropy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now he has a university in Budapest among many other things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, of course, he is very controversial because no good deed goes unpunished, and he has done many good deeds.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When I first went back-- first of all, I've been going back to Hungary regularly since 1964, so I'm really the only American Hungarian who, for the last 32 years, every single year has been back and heavily involved.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "First, it's just a professor and an interested person, but the last 16 years in a political sense.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I have tried to do a great deal for strengthening democracy in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
